data.description: Don't miss this 2 bd/2ba home in a great 55+ community in the valley. Moffitt Court Association is centrally located for all your needs and wants. You'll find a nice patio and fenced backyard. This home had a newer roof in 2015, new hot water tank in 2020, new garage door and AC unit in 2021 along with the primary shower being remodeled in 2021. Great natural light in the living space and primary bedroom. The HOA will take care of the lawn and snow removal.
